#

Honey Glazed Beef Stir-Fry

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Stir-FryQuick MealAsian-Inspired

Description

A vibrant stir-fry featuring tender beef and seasonal vegetables, coated in a sweet and savory honey glaze.

Ingredients

  • Beef sirloin: 1 lb, sliced thin
  • Bell peppers: 1 cup, assorted colors, sliced
  • Broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • Carrots: 1 cup, thinly sliced
  • Onion: 1 medium, sliced
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Cornstarch: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp, for garnish

9/19/2024
